summary:
Calls on the Turkish Cypriot side and Turkish forces to restore the military status quo in Strovilia as of 30 June 2000 (para 7);

 Requests a report from the Secretary-General on implementation by 1 December 2007 (para 8);

 Welcomes UNFICYP's efforts to implement zero tolerance policy on sexual exploitation and abuse, and requests the Secretary-General to keep the Council informed (para 9);

 Decides to remain seized of the matter (para 10).
